      • main

        public static void main(java.lang.String[] args)
                 throws java.lang.Exception
        This main method is only for testing purposes. It runs the reader on Knowtator directories. Expects directory named "Knowtator" and a sibling directory "Knowtator_XML". "Knowtator" should have a subdirectory called "text" containing plaintext files "Knowtator_XML" should have files that end with .knowtator.xml
